{
  "stem": "1917.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so next day, I came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at this time, I was not afraid anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I became a very, very good organizer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I-- we had potatoes three or four times a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We would boil them in little pots in the evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had a little brigade of organizers that would stand guard so the supervisors wouldn't find us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We organized coal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we would-- one would boil the potatoes, and the other one would use the same pot-- without any salt, with the skin.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the steady diet of potatoes cured Miriam, or at least helped-- got-- got her a lot stronger.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She got rid of her dysentery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we didn't know at the time, but she suffered from severe kidney infection.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Toward the end of the summer, the gypsy camp was eliminated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were taken into the gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the rumor was, of course, that we would be next.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "As far as the experiments are concerned, what I know about the experiment-- there were two distinct type of experiment that were done on me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there were some other experiments that were done on older children-- on teenagers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "In our case, part of the experiment was done in the blood lab.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The problem was not only was the blood taking that made us very weak, but with the shot, the injections, that were given into the arm-- that were germs of all sorts of kind.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were all kind of other tests that they were running.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know that the twins were used and were injected with all kind of chemicals and germs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What they were, we do not know up to date.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other part of the experiments were done in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
